The article is a statement issued by President Donald Trump to the Congress of the United States. In the statement, President Trump reports that he has issued an Executive Order regarding Iran. The order aims to deny Iran revenue that could be used to fund its nuclear program, missile development, terrorism, and malign regional influence. The order also blocks the property and interests in property of individuals determined by the Secretary of the Treasury, in consultation with the Secretary of State. The President delegates the authority to the Secretary of the Treasury, in consultation with the Secretary of State, to take necessary actions to implement the order. A copy of the order is enclosed with the statement.